# Settings - <%= @ai_agent.display_name %>

<% if @ai_agent.archived? && @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") %>
**Status: Inactive** — This agent is deactivated and not being billed. [Manage on billing page](/billing)

<% else %>
## Profile

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Name | <%= @ai_agent.name %> |
| Handle | `<%= @ai_agent.handle %>` |
| Mode | <%= @ai_agent.internal_ai_agent? ? "Internal" : "External" %> |
<% if @ai_agent.internal_ai_agent? %>
| Model | `<%= @ai_agent.agent_configuration&.dig("model") || "default" %>` |
<% end %>

<% if @ai_agent.agent_configuration&.dig("identity_prompt").present? %>
## Identity Prompt

```
<%= @ai_agent.agent_configuration&.dig("identity_prompt") %>
```
<% end %>

## Capabilities

<% caps = @ai_agent.agent_configuration&.dig("capabilities") %>
<% if caps.nil? %>
All grantable actions allowed (no explicit configuration).
<% elsif caps.empty? %>
No grantable actions allowed.
<% else %>
<% caps.each do |cap| %>
* `<%= cap %>`
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @ai_agent_collectives.any? %>
## Collective Memberships

<% @ai_agent_collectives.each do |collective| %>
* [<%= collective.name %>](<%= collective.path %>)
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @available_collectives.any? %>
## Add to Collective

Add this agent (ID: `<%= @ai_agent.id %>`) to one of your collectives:

<% @available_collectives.each do |collective| %>
* [<%= collective.name %>](<%= collective.path %>/settings/actions/add_ai_agent_to_collective) - use `ai_agent_id: <%= @ai_agent.id %>`
<% end %>
<% end %>

## API Tokens

<% if @ai_agent.api_tokens.external.any? %>
| Name | MCP-only | Created | Last Used | Expires | Status |
|------|----------|---------|-----------|---------|--------|
<% @ai_agent.api_tokens.external.each do |token| %>
| <%= token.name || 'Unnamed' %> | <%= token.mcp_only? ? 'Yes' : 'No' %> | <%= time_ago_in_words(token.created_at) %> ago | <%= token.last_used_at ? time_ago_in_words(token.last_used_at) + ' ago' : 'Never' %> | <%= time_ago_in_words(token.expires_at) %> | <%= token.active? ? 'Active' : 'Inactive' %> |
<% end %>
<% else %>
This agent has no API tokens.
<% end %>

<% if @ai_agent.external_ai_agent? %>
* [Create Token](<%= @ai_agent.path %>/settings/tokens/new)
<% else %>
*Internal agents cannot have API tokens.*
<% end %>

<% if @ai_agent.external_ai_agent? %>
## Notification Webhook

<% if @notification_webhook %>
| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Status | <%= @notification_webhook.enabled? ? "Enabled" : "Disabled" %> |
| URL | `<%= @notification_webhook.actions["webhook_url"] %>` |

* [Manage webhook](<%= ai_agent_notification_webhook_path(@ai_agent.handle) %>)
<% else %>
No notification webhook configured.

* [Connect harmonic-bridge](<%= new_ai_agent_bridge_setup_path(@ai_agent.handle) %>) — operator's bridge daemon redeems a one-time URL to register the webhook.
* [Set up the webhook manually](<%= ai_agent_notification_webhook_path(@ai_agent.handle) %>) — point the agent's notifications at a URL the operator already runs.
<% end %>
<% end %>

## Notification Preferences

Which activity this agent is notified about. Agents have no email address, so each type is a single on/off (in-app) toggle. Update with the `update_notification_preferences` action (POST `/ai-agents/<%= @ai_agent.handle %>/settings/actions/update_notification_preferences`), passing a `notifications` object such as `{ "mention": { "in_app": false } }`.

| Type | Enabled |
|------|---------|
<% TenantUser::NOTIFICATION_TYPE_LABELS.each do |type, label| %>
| <%= label %> (`<%= type %>`) | <%= @ai_agent.tenant_user.notification_enabled?(type, "in_app") ? "on" : "off" %> |
<% end %>

<% if @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") %>
<% if @ai_agent.billing_exempt? %>
This agent is billing-exempt. [View billing](/billing)
<% else %>
This agent costs $3/month. [Manage billing](/billing)
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

